  rotate=0.0
]{$y = x^2$};

  scale=0.5,
  anchor=base west,
  text=blue,
  rotate=0.0
]{$y = (x+2)^2$};

  scale=0.5,
  anchor=base west,
  text=green,
  rotate=0.0
]{$y = (x-2)^2$};
